> Hi, i'm also going through the same problem. But, it would not be viable in my case to open and close the file. Would anyone have another solution? Any way to not need to have this validation?

You can modify the code in the library yourself.

```
          case 'docProps/app.xml': {
            const appXform = new AppXform();
            const appProperties = await appXform.parseStream(stream);
            model.company = appProperties ? appProperties.company : 'Company';
            model.manager = appProperties ? appProperties.manager : 'Manager';
            break;
          }
```
          
        Path: node_modules\exceljs\lib\xlsx\xlsx.js
